<div class="body">
<b1 style="font-size=200%;font-family:'News Cycle';color:'black';text-align:center;">
  <i style="text-align:center">Check back soon for improvements!</i>
  <IMG href="/" SRC="https://orig00.deviantart.net/9824/f/2015/113/c/f/pug_by_luczynski-d8qqowk.gif">
